dr.evolution.alignment
Class Patterns

java.lang.Object
  dr.evolution.alignment.Patterns
All Implemented Interfaces:
PatternList, TaxonList, Identifiable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Taxon>
public class Patterns
extends java.lang.Object
implements PatternList

A concrete implementation of PatternList. Patterns can be added and removed from the list individually or in bulk from an alignment.
